videos.description: Tim Legler breaks down whether he was more surprised by Stephen Curry scoring 40 points or Anthony Davis struggling in the Warriors' 111-95 victory over the Pelicans.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Curry or Davis the bigger surprise on opening night?) 2015/10/27 SC

videos.description: Stephen Curry catches up with Marc Stein to reveal his championship ring and break down his 24-point first quarter in the Warriors' 111-95 victory over the Pelicans.
